videos.headline: Miami off to a quick start with 44-yard TD
videos.description: RB Mark Walton turns on the afterburners and scores on a 44-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Walton already over 100 rush yards in game
videos.description: The Hurricanes' offensive line creates a huge hole for Mark Walton to gain 82 yards.

videos.headline: Hand-eye coordination lessons by Miami Harley on a juggling catch
videos.description: It takes a few tries, but WR Mike Harley is finally able to corral this catch.

videos.headline: Toledo has some movement with Swanson 26-yard carry
videos.description: RB Terry Swanson shimmies and shakes to gain 26 yards for good field position.

videos.headline: Rockets take the lead on 37-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Logan Woodside finds WR Jon'Vea Johnson wide open on the right side for a 37-yard touchdown to take the lead.

videos.headline: Miami caps off great drive with rushing TD to take the lead
videos.description: RB Travis Homer finds the gap and scores from 12 yards out to regain the lead.

videos.headline: Berrios changes direction on a dime and gains 55
videos.description: WR Braxton Berrios makes the catch and goes the opposite way for a huge gain for Miami.

videos.headline: Lob pass leads to TD snag for Miami
videos.description: QB Malik Rosier tosses it up and WR Dayall Harris goes up and pulls down the pass for a touchdown to extend the Canes' lead.

videos.headline: Give him the turnover chain!
videos.description: Toledo QB Logan Woodside loses grip on the ball and Miami's Sheldrick Redwine is there to scoop it up for the recovery and then wears the chain to celebrate.

videos.headline: Miami taking control at home with pass TD
videos.description: QB Malik Rosier finds WR Braxton Berrios in the back of the endzone to boost the Hurricanes' lead to 15.

videos.headline: Miami is firing on all cylinders with another pass TD
videos.description: QB Malik Rosier connects with Christopher Herndon IV for his third passing touchdown of the day.

videos.headline: Toledo is hanging tough adding another pass TD
videos.description: The Rockets' deficit is cut to 16 after QB Logan Woodside connects with Diontae Johnson for the score.

videos.headline: Toledo's interception gives them great field position
videos.description: QB Malik Rosier throws his first interception as a starter for Miami and it gives Toledo a redzone opportunity.

videos.headline: A stellar catch gets Toledo to within 8
videos.description: QB Logan Woodside, again, finds WR Diontae Johnson for 8-yard toe dragging catch.

videos.headline: Rosier adds a rushing TD after 3 passing TDs
videos.description: Miami QB Malik Rosier keeps it and scores from 23-yards out to give the Hurricanes some comfort in their lead.

videos.headline: Homer rushing TD delivers knockout punch for Miami
videos.description: RB Travis Homer finds some running room on the right side and sneaks in to the endzone.
